{"tid":221093,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[巴絲都入]同對方好唔夾，但重好鍾意對方，應唔應該分手？","createTime":"2017-04-28T12:37:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-30T12:44:22.000Z","uid":72462,"like":5,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"18abaacc0c1284aa6e077c123b5beac07520dd71","tid":221093,"uid":72462,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:37:25.000Z","msg":"是咁的，其實大家都重好鍾意對方。但性格上兩個都係比較硬（？），一鬧交就會傷害到對方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時又口硬心軟咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞到鬧一次交都搞大半日。<br />\n可能大家真係唔適合係埋一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  你地有無試過好唔夾都一齊緊既成功例子/失敗例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 分 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔分"},{"pid":"45e4b9cd3e74619c279a45c690bec5b7a80323c5","tid":221093,"uid":72462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:39:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28062a45852a099d0cc30528a19aa047fb18cfd1","tid":221093,"uid":72462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:42:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6648fc0d99aad6249bca002f9360d5dac443ebe","tid":221093,"uid":20696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:51:47.000Z","msg":"見絲打你之前話你男朋友對你好好喎，就咁放手真係捨得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實再夾嘅情侶都會嗌交，未必咁就係唔適合，又唔好咁快就諗住放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但講啲野hurt對方長遠黎講真係好傷感情，或者你兩個都可以一齊改，再嬲有啲野都唔可以講出口。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw我覺得愛一個人根本唔會捨得傷害佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即使有時只係一時衝動火遮眼，但講出口嘅說話覆水難收，大家都會有條刺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b88ed86010263cb76f1d694cb2aa851840fc42","tid":221093,"uid":104260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:53:53.000Z","msg":"咁可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔夾唔夾都唔過左2年<br />\n係睇2個人點就<br />\n得一個人肯改就收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4440ebc5d63ff3aa10cd5dacdccc894f9abe1749","tid":221093,"uid":72462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:58:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見絲打你之前話你男朋友對你好好喎，就咁放手真係捨得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實再夾嘅情侶都會嗌交，未必咁就係唔適合，又唔好咁快就諗住放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但講啲野hurt對方長遠黎講真係好傷感情，或者你兩個都可以一齊改，再嬲有啲野都唔可以講出口。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nbtw我覺得愛一個人根本唔會捨得傷害佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即使有時只係一時衝動火遮眼，但講出口嘅說話覆水難收，大家都會有條刺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我唔係絲打本人，借左佢AC <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似精神分裂咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n無鬧交但一齊西面西半日，大家都好攰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fdadc11dda4307807ca53b657da7dc78ca72447","tid":221093,"uid":72462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T12:58:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔夾唔夾都唔過左2年<br />\n係睇2個人點就<br />\n得一個人肯改就收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n肯改但又係咁發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa00403cfe31b7e68f2abef07474ae1217fd7aa4","tid":221093,"uid":75026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:06:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47f6eb89a520e5b134a644471175e8676b603033","tid":221093,"uid":104260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:14:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔夾唔夾都唔過左2年<br />\n係睇2個人點就<br />\n得一個人肯改就收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n肯改但又係咁發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁就唔係肯改<br />\n根本就係把口講<br />\n得把死人口<br />\n我都心淡啦<br />\n事但啦<br />\n唔改就唔改啦<br />\n磨到我唔中意你為止啦"},{"pid":"e8e2620ad46577b6e0b5a57dbae3e8d8da0c5446","tid":221093,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:19:24.000Z","msg":"個人認為只要互相鍾意 肯為對方犧牲 無野解決唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n楊過同小龍女夠唔夾啦 一個好靜一個好熱鬧<br />\n但大家都肯同理對方 同埋留意到對方需要並作出配合<br />\n如果作要你作出既犧牲唔成正比 咁咪佢唔夠愛你囉"},{"pid":"f5c6fcc6931870312cdb715d483ca92da744ae45","tid":221093,"uid":14440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:20:35.000Z","msg":"性格影響行為但不決定行為 唔好拎性格黎做藉口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正如冬天唔想起身 咪又係靠意志力起到身"},{"pid":"f4629a296856d69ca550d3d06af5a14602112627","tid":221093,"uid":10141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:20:37.000Z","msg":"負評！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好分手呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果真係鐘意大家，點解唔可以去改變自己<br />\n你話有去改，但係改唔到，咁得把口冇用架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好冇咗先去後悔，一定要好好珍惜大家呀<br />\n兩個人點都會有磨擦<br />\n但係要有啲火花先磨合到兩個唔同嘅人<br />\n係愛佢就唔好灰心呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2952763af01e914e409e52f603935a7fcb73240b","tid":221093,"uid":108651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T13:30:29.000Z","msg":"巴打 我都係同樣情況 係性格不合嘅情況下拍左5 6年 最後都分左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 奉勸你同佢認真傾一傾 如果大家傾完都係得把口講點改點改 咁就長痛不如短痛啦 咁當然感情係要磨合 應該盡力去維繫嘅 未到最後關頭都唔好講分手啊 加油巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3048887c412f5b3fa44dce48a97215090b97ec91","tid":221093,"uid":72462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:22:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打 我都係同樣情況 係性格不合嘅情況下拍左5 6年 最後都分左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 奉勸你同佢認真傾一傾 如果大家傾完都係得把口講點改點改 咁就長痛不如短痛啦 咁當然感情係要磨合 應該盡力去維繫嘅 未到最後關頭都唔好講分手啊 加油巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最後雙方都太辛苦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8dd1b13072b86a17de9aa54299aabd1a48f32216","tid":221093,"uid":72462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T16:23:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>負評！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好分手呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果真係鐘意大家，點解唔可以去改變自己<br />\n你話有去改，但係改唔到，咁得把口冇用架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔好冇咗先去後悔，一定要好好珍惜大家呀<br />\n兩個人點都會有磨擦<br />\n但係要有啲火花先磨合到兩個唔同嘅人<br />\n係愛佢就唔好灰心呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果大家努力完都係咁呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f128c57e24167e332558fec80bc69a21f30b1f","tid":221093,"uid":108651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T22:11:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>巴打 我都係同樣情況 係性格不合嘅情況下拍左5 6年 最後都分左手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 奉勸你同佢認真傾一傾 如果大家傾完都係得把口講點改點改 咁就長痛不如短痛啦 咁當然感情係要磨合 應該盡力去維繫嘅 未到最後關頭都唔好講分手啊 加油巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n最後雙方都太辛苦？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以巴打你真係要諗清楚 如果有得比重新黎過 我情願同佢做朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef9b5a6f42bd9a4b69fa20b94fe5c26806926ba0","tid":221093,"uid":105955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T11:54:05.000Z","msg":"我都係 同男朋友<br />\n性格完全唔夾<br />\n佢鐘意同一班識既人玩 同一班識既人返工<br />\n但我咩都想去識下 咩都接觸下<br />\n做野又係 佢只要覺得個個都唔做<br />\n佢唔會曬時間做落去<br />\n而我就係只要開左個頭就要做落去既人<br />\n我地大家都見過大家既屋企人<br />\n佢屋企人叫我去食飯我一定出現<br />\n但我屋企人叫佢就死都唔去<br />\n<br />\n仲有每次嗌親交<br />\n佢就永遠唔出聲<br />\n我就好似癲婆咁鬧佢<br />\n<br />\n利申：今日又嗌緊啦"},{"pid":"0fca266acaee9e140b3555ac54f5d375ba551890","tid":221093,"uid":100442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T11:59:15.000Z","msg":"我係雞"},{"pid":"7f876d04fafee26922dde668be9d15eed15d5bf6","tid":221093,"uid":26823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T12:02:01.000Z","msg":"同你一樣 已分手<br />\n一齊既時候一星期鬧一次 好辛苦<br />\n散左唔開心一排 但完全冇後悔<br />\n磨合講既係大家改到既野<br />\n性格太硬根本改唔到 只能夠係一邊不停忍"},{"pid":"de9ba20e9a5d88d164ed3ed0c15bd5d875e99943","tid":221093,"uid":106604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T12:07:40.000Z","msg":"比人飛左<br />\n未試過解決佢就話解決唔到<br />\n點解咁易放棄"},{"pid":"d12820a0dd3cc4b6501cc58d6c694935a197b5a7","tid":221093,"uid":21662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T12:11:33.000Z","msg":"同樓主差唔多，最近分左手。<br />\n<br />\n以過來人黎講，我覺得最重要都係follow your heart ，大家都鍾意既，無論點辛苦都會一齊到落去。<br />\n<br />\n但只要是但有一方冇左個個心，點樣維繫都冇用。<br />\n<br />\n你話講野傷害到大家，其實只要誠心道歉，我相信都會原諒。最緊要都係有野就要講，諗緊咩唔好收收埋埋，有咩就攞出黎講。始終兩個人都係獨立個體，意見有唔同好合理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔好放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d9e57a4e5e4a6485fcaceeffc03c55677aa0f3","tid":221093,"uid":112938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T12:44:22.000Z","msg":"既然明知呢個係唔好既性格, 點解唔試下改?<br />\n你真係鍾意佢 唔想大家因為咁唔開心既<br />\n咁咪試下改"}]}